# Source Of Truth

## Purpose
Canonical reference for local runtime behavior, ports, and lifecycle commands.

## Canonical Ports
- Backend API: `8080`
- Frontend static app: `8090`

## Canonical URLs
- Frontend: `http://localhost:8090`
- Backend health: `http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health`
- Backend feed: `http://localhost:8080/api/v1/feed/articles`
- Backend mock AI: `http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai/mock`

## Lifecycle Commands
From repo root:
```bash
make down || true
make up
make status
make health
```

## Validation Rules
- PID files:
  - `.run/backend.pid`
  - `.run/frontend.pid`
- Authoritative PID source: `lsof -tiTCP:<port> -sTCP:LISTEN | head -n1`
- Do not silently reuse unknown processes occupying required ports.
